2>Applications of System of Equations</h2>
</div>
<p>Systems of equations are a very useful tool and find application in our =
day-to-day lives for modeling real-life situations and analyzing questions =
about them.</p>
<p><strong>=E2=98=9BCheck:</strong></p>
