 class=3D"collapsed-answer" itemtype=3D"https://schema.org/Answer"><div ite=
mprop=3D"text"><p>Solving system of equations is finding the values of vari=
ables that satisfy each equation in that system. There are three main metho=
ds to solving system of equations, they are:</p><ul>
<li>Substitution Method</li>
<li>Cross-multiplication method</li>
<li>Elimination Method</li>
<li>Graphical Method</li>
</ul></div></div></div><div itemscope=3D"" class=3D"collapsed-question" ite=
